metadata.name: BIRD OF A DIFFERENT FEATHER
metadata.description:
Bird with a different feather
Wading through the breeze
With a coat unlike any other,
That sets it apart with ease.

With its unique path,
And its one of a kind way
It soars through the waves
With no need to sway.

For it knows that it's different,
And it embraces its own,
With a heart full of courage,
And a spirit that's flown.

So let us be all like,
The bird with a different feather,
Embracing our own uniqueness,
And soaring together.
